author: By PAUL WISEMAN and ANNE D'INNOCENZIO AP Business Writers
title: After virus fades, service industries may be changed forever
description: WASHINGTON (AP) — For years, personal trainer Amanda Tikalsky didn’t have to worry much about her job. The U.S. economy’s record-breaking 11-year expansion offered security to service workers like her.
